org.apache.flink.queryablestate.client.state

类 ImmutableMapState<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.queryablestate.client.state.ImmutableState
      • org.apache.flink.queryablestate.client.state.ImmutableMapState<K,V>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MapState<K,V>, State

    @PublicEvolving
public final class ImmutableMapState<K,V>
extends ImmutableState
implements MapState<K,V>
    A read-only MapState that does not allow for modifications.

    This is the result returned when querying Flink's keyed state using the Queryable State Client and providing an MapStateDescriptor.
